children.text: 1.7 While taking note of the constant trend of reduction in
Proposed Allocation versus Actual Allocation of
funds, both at the BE and RE Stages, the
Committee desired the Department to actively
pursue with the Ministry of Finance to increase
allocation of funds to the Department for the
justifications for seeking increased allocation of
funds for Major Schemes during the year 2020-21
have also been readily provided by the Department.
